---
// Server ran / terminal ran code
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro'

---
<SiteLayout>
	<article>
      <main>
				<section class="intro">
					<img src="/img/fluffmonster.png" alt="a bat that with flowers and colors around it" width="200">
					<p>So you somehow found your way here. That's one more than the zero I expected</p>
					<p>So I guess I should probably say some words, I dunno, about either the site or myself. Perhaps both?</p>
					<p>Over time I'll probably/maybe/depends improve this site, add some more stuff, maybe a portfolio when I have enough stuff for an actual portfolio</p>
				</section>
    </main>
  </article>

	<article>
		<section class="about-me">
			<header>
				<h2>About Me</h2>
			</header>
			<main>
				<p>I'm a 30-something he/him who currently resides in Barcelona.</p>
				<p>I'm interested in a bunch of stuff, for example:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>History</li>
					<li>Archaeology</li>
					<li>Philosophy</li>
					<li>Anarchism</li>
					<li>Music, of most kinds</li>
					<li>Knowledge, of just about any kind</li>
				</ul>
				<p>I ply my trade at a small Dev Studio hiring ourselves out to clients and working on some inhouse projects. Mostly front-end, but also anything really.</p>
		</main>
		</section>	
	</article>

	<article>
		<section>
			<header>
				<h2>Projects</h2>
			</header>
			<main>
				<ul>
					<li>Well, this website I guess</li>
					<li>The Historic Temperature/Weather graphs</li>
					<li>Running a small self-hosted nextcloud/mastdon/etc server for me and my friends</li>
					<li>Expanding this list</li>
				</ul>
				<p>Should probably mention, the data for the graphs comes from <a href="https://open-meteo.com/">Open Meteo</a> </p>
			</main>
		</section>
	</article>
	
	<article>
		<section class="tech">
			<header>
			<h2>Tech stuff</h2>
		</header>
		<main>
			<p>Site is built using:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Astro</li>
				<li>Some Vue</li>
				<li>Chart.js for the Graphs</li>
				<li>Thoughts and prayers</li>
			</ul>
		</main>
		</section>
	</article>
</SiteLayout>
<style>
	article:first-of-type {
		margin-top: 5rem;
	}
  article {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 70%;
    background-color:  hsl(220, 50%, 95%);
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    display: grid;
    grid-column-start:  2;
    place-self: start center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  article main {
    padding: 1rem;
    display: grid;
  }
  article main img {
		border-radius: 5px;
  }
	article h3 {
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 60%;
    place-self: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  article ul {
		list-style: square;
		margin-block: 1rem;
		margin-left: 3rem;
  }
  article p {
		margin-block: 0.5rem;
  }
	section header {
		text-align: center;
		padding-block: 1rem;
		background-color:rebeccapurple;
		color: whitesmoke;
	}
  .intro {
		display: grid;
  }
  .intro img {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		margin-inline: auto;
  }
  a {
		text-decoration:  none;
		color: purple;
  }
</style>